Class CourseSection

  • java.lang.Object
    • CourseSection

  • public class CourseSection
extends java.lang.Object
    One section of a course

    One course can have many sections. This class represents one section for one course. The course is identified by its id.

    Author:
    Phil O'Connell (pxo4@psu.edu)
